    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h4><i>Enjoy Mexico and the Caribbean for less</i></h4>
        <p>
            Save 15% on base fares or save $150 per booking with Air Canada Vacations® 
            when you travel to Mexico or the Caribbean. 
            <pre>Book by Feb. 6, 2019.</pre>
        </p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="">Book Now &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h4><i>California</i></h4>
        <p>
            Travel to the tropics in style with our new comfort fare and enjoy access to
            a Preferred Seat, a complimentary alcoholic beverage, and more.
            <pre>Travel until June 15, 2019.</pre>
        </p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="">Book Now &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h4>Phoenix Sale</h4>
        <p>For a limited-time, save on your California getaway. <pre>Book by February 5, 2019.</pre></p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=301867">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
</div>
